    Note over User,Operator: Flow 1: FeatureStore Reconciliation
    User->>K8s: Create FeatureStore CR (feast.dev/v1)
    K8s->>Operator: Watch event (SA Token auth)
    Operator->>K8s: Create Deployment, Services,<br/>ConfigMaps, PVC, SA, CronJob<br/>HTTPS/TLS, SA Token
    Operator->>K8s: Create Route (OpenShift, UI only)<br/>HTTPS/TLS, SA Token

    Note over MLApp,DB: Flow 2: Feature Serving (Online)
    MLApp->>Online: GET/POST features<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, K8s RBAC or OIDC
    Online->>DB: Query backend (optional)<br/>TLS, Secret credentials
    DB-->>Online: Feature data
    Online-->>MLApp: Feature values (JSON)

    Note over User,Deploy: Flow 3: CronJob Feature Materialization
    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        participant CronJob as CronJob Pod<br/>ose-cli
        K8s->>CronJob: Trigger on schedule
        CronJob->>K8s: kubectl exec<br/>443/TCP HTTPS, SA Token
        K8s->>Deploy: exec channel (RBAC)
        Deploy->>Deploy: feast apply /<br/>feast materialize-incremental
    end

    Note over User,Registry: Flow 4: Notebook Integration
    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
